## A demo scripts to generate Chakra ET with STAGE and simulate through AstraSIM

### Steps:
- Prepare astra-sim docker: `bash prepare_astra_sim.sh`, and it will start an interactive container
- Prepare STAGE within docker: INSIDE container (and all followsing steps are inside container), `bash prepare_stage.sh`
- Generate Workloads: `bash generate_workload.sh`
- (Optional) Visualize generated Chakra ETs: `chakra_visualizer --input_filename ./workloads/toy_arws.0.et --output_filename ./workloads/toy_arws.0.pdf`
- Run simulation through AstraSim: `bash run_astrasim.sh`, and the results will be saved in `*.stdout`